data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! This charming residence boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms within its spacious 1,281 square feet. The moment you step inside, you'll be greeted by the grandeur of a cathedral ceiling in the living area, creating an open and airy atmosphere.

The well-appointed kitchen comes complete with all appliances, making meal preparation a breeze. Enjoy the seamless flow of the open floor plan, with hardwood flooring throughout, adding a touch of warmth and elegance to every room.

A partially finished basement provides additional space for your creative touch or extra storage. Step outside onto the inviting back deck and take in the breathtaking mountain views, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. With a location close to downtown, convenience meets tranquility in this lovely home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this residence your own slice of paradise! *Information deemed reliable, but not guaranteed. Buyer/Buyer's agent to verify all information.*
